                    "frequency": "once per hour",
                    "effect": "You conjure a shard of Nirvana in a 30 foot emanation , temporarily altering the landscape into an soothing meadow for 1 minute. Creatures in the area gain a +1 item bonus to Will saves and Wisdom-based skill checks, and have fast healing 2. A creature in the area that attempts to take a hostile action must succeed at a DC 28 Will save or the hostile action is prevented and the actions they would\u2019ve spent are wasted.",
